Money.item_description: Currency traded on Palpagos Island. Can be exchanged for items or Pals with merchants.

Arrow.item_description: An Arrow for use with a bow.

Arrow_Poison.item_description: Arrows to use with a Poison Bow. They will poison any target hit.

Arrow_Fire.item_description: An Arrow for use with a Fire Bow. Deals Fire damage.

AssaultRifle_Default1.item_description: An Assault Rifle suited to long range combat. It excels at rapid-fire and is well suited to taking down powerful foes.

Axe_Tier_00.item_description: An axe for cutting wood. Made from stone, it's not very sharp.

Axe_Tier_01.item_description: An axe for cutting wood. Made from metal, its sharpness has improved.

Axe_Tier_02.item_description: An axe for cutting wood. Made from high quality metal, its sharpness has improved even further.

Bat.item_description: A Wooden Club for close range combat. Fighting a Pal with it might be tough.

Bat2.item_description: Baseball bat for close-range combat. Might be tough to get a home run with a Pal.

MeatCutterKnife.item_description:
Knife for butchering Pals. When equipped, the Pet command becomes Butcher.
Butchered Pals will not return.

ElecBaton.item_description:
A baton with electricity running through it. It can shock a Pal, stopping it in its tracks.
Electrocuted Pals are easier to capture.

Berries.item_description: A versatile ingredient that is delicious raw or cooked. They can be found anywhere on the island.

Baked_Berries.item_description: Cooking enhances their nutritional value, and surprisingly, they are quite filling.

BowGun.item_description: This can be used to fire Arrows effortlessly. Its power more than makes up for its slow reload time.

Charcoal.item_description: Charcoal made from burning Wood. It can be combined with Sulfur to create Gunpowder.

Cloth.item_description: Cloth woven from Wool. Required to create armor.

Cloth2.item_description: High Quality Cloth woven from a large amount of Wool. Required to create high quality armor.

ClothArmor.item_description: Clothes made from Cloth. Protects against the cold of night.

Coal.item_description: Coal often found in caves and other places. Required to create high quality metal.

CopperArmor.item_description: Armor made of metal. Its sheer weight speaks to its sturdiness.

CopperHelmet.item_description: A helm made of metal. A reliable piece of armor that protects your head, and all the thoughts within.

CopperIngot.item_description: A material required to create metal weapons and armor. Refined from Ore using a furnace.

CopperOre.item_description:
Becomes an ingot when refined using a furnace. Can be found in caves and other places.
There are rumors of Pals capable of detecting ore.

DoubleBarrelShotgun.item_description: A shotgun ideal for close range combat. Despite the limited load capacity, it still packs a punch.

ExplosiveBullet.item_description: Ammo for Rocket Launcher and other similar weapons.

Fiber.item_description: Fiber collected from trees. A material used when creating bows, etc.

Flint.item_description: A material required to start a fire. Can sometimes be found when excavating rocks.

FurArmor.item_description: Armor made from Leather. Its warmth and defense have been improved.

FurHelmet.item_description: A beautiful feathered headband. Though improbable, it somehow seems to protect its wearer from lethal head injuries.

GrilledMeat.item_description: Grilled meat. A full stomach leads to smiling faces.

Gunpowder2.item_description: Gunpowder used to fire ammunition. Required to make bullets.

HandGun_Default.item_description: Pistol with improved capacity and rapid-fire capabilities. Has more immediate firepower than a Makeshift Handgun.

DecalGun_1.item_description: Strange gun that paints a picture of Cattiva where it is fired. Have some fun and paint the walls or ceilings!

DecalGun_2.item_description: Strange gun that paints a picture of Lamball where it is fired. Have some fun and paint the walls or ceilings!

DecalGun_3.item_description: Strange gun that paints a picture of Melpaca where it is fired. Have some fun and paint the walls or ceilings!

DecalGun_4.item_description: Strange gun that paints a picture of Anubis where it is fired. Have some fun and paint the walls or ceilings!

DecalGun_5.item_description: Strange gun that paints a picture of Relaxaurus where it is fired. Have some fun and paint the walls or ceilings!

Herbs.item_description: Low Grade Medical Supplies good for colds and sprains. They don't heal HP when eaten, however.

Medicines.item_description: Strange Medical Supplies that are effective at treating Ulcer and Fracture. they do not heal Health.

LuxuryMedicines.item_description: High Grade Medical Supplies that are effective at treating Weakened and Depressed. they do not heal Health.

MindControlDrug.item_description: Mind Control Meds that are extremely effective in controlling dissidents. they do not heal Health.

Poppy.item_description: A plant that blooms colorful flowers. Can be used to make Suspicious Juice and Strange Juice.

Opium.item_description:
Juice that improves mood when consumed. Drinking it greatly increases work speed for a period of time,
but lowers SAN.

Narcotic.item_description:
Juice that greatly improves mood when consumed. Drinking it significantly increases work speed for a period of time,
but significantly lowers SAN.

StatusPointResetSan.item_description: A potion that allows the player to reset status points when consumed. It has no effect if consumed by Pal.

HomingSphereLauncher.item_description: A launcher for firing spheres. Fired spheres home in on Pals.

IronArmor.item_description: Armor made from high quality metal. It boasts high defense, if you can bear the weight.

IronHelmet.item_description: A helm made from high quality metal. The luster from the polished metal gives the wearer that added boost of confidence.

IronIngot.item_description: A material required to create high quality metal weapons and armor. Refined from Ore and Coal using a furnace.

Launcher_Default.item_description: A Rocket Launcher. It can fire powerful rounds from long distances.

Leather.item_description: Leather taken from a Pal, it serves as a defensive material. It can be obtained from certain Pals.

MachineParts.item_description: Necessary for building various facilities. Can be made with a Primitive Workbench.

MachineParts2.item_description: Required to create precision equipment. Can be made with a High Quality Workbench.

Meat.item_description: Pal meat. Its so fresh that even a human could safely eat it raw.

PalSphere.item_description: An item that captures Pals when thrown. Mass produced, it is only effective on low level Pals.

PalSphere_Mega.item_description: An item that captures Pals when thrown. Its capabilities have been improved, allowing it to catch a wider range of Pals.

PalSphere_Giga.item_description: A sphere that captures Pals when thrown. Able to capture moderately powerful Pals.

PalSphere_Tera.item_description: A sphere that captures Pals when thrown. Able to capture very powerful Pals.

PalSphere_Master.item_description: A sphere that captures Pals when thrown. With powerful abilities, not many Pals are able to escape it.

PalSphere_Legend.item_description:
A sphere that captures Pals when thrown. It has extremely powerful capturing capabilities,
leaving almost no Pal able to escape.

PalSphere_Robbery.item_description:
A sphere that captures Pals when thrown. Though it has a low chance of success,
it can forcibly capture another persons Pal.

Pan.item_description: Bread made from baked Flour. A tasty staple food.

Pickaxe_Tier_00.item_description: A pickaxe used for mining. Made from stone, the efficiency is questionable.

Pickaxe_Tier_01.item_description: A pickaxe used for mining. Made from metal, the durability and efficiency have improved.

Pickaxe_Tier_02.item_description: A pickaxe used for mining. Its durability and sharpness have increased even more.

PumpActionShotgun.item_description: A high capacity, powerful shotgun. It has outstanding close range DPS.

SingleShotRifle.item_description: A single-shot rifle. What it lacks in capacity, it makes up for with sheer power.

InkBullet.item_description: Ammo for a Decal Gun. Uses ink to paint a picture of a Pal.

HandgunBullet.item_description: Bullets used in items like Handgun.

RifleBullet.item_description: Bullets used in rifles and similar firearms.

ShotgunBullet.item_description: Bullets used in shotguns and similar firearms.

RoughBullet.item_description: Ammo for Musket, Makeshift Handgun, and other similar weapons.

MachinegunBullet.item_description: Ammo for {item-name-missing} and other similar weapons.

AssaultRifleBullet.item_description: Ammo for Assault Rifle and other similar weapons.

MagnumBullet.item_description: Ammo for {item-name-missing} and other similar weapons.

SphereLauncher.item_description: A new type of launcher that fires a large number of spheres. It can easily capture a herd of Pals.

SphereLauncher_Once.item_description: A launcher that fires spheres. It can capture Pals that are a distance away.

StealArmor.item_description:
Armor made from Pal Metal Ingot. High defense, but extremely heavy.
Equipment for a hero, it exudes bravery.

StealHelmet.item_description: A helm made from Pal Metal Ingot. Envied for its immaculate quality, it is proof of a chosen warrior.

StealIngot.item_description: Material required to create weapons and armor using Pal Metal. Made stronger by creating an alloy from metal and Paldium.

Stone.item_description: Material for structures and items. Can be obtained by mining rocks.

Pal_crystal_S.item_description: Crystallized energy from the World Tree. Capable of creating supernatural items and structures.

PAL_Growth_Stone_S.item_description: A mysterious stone that can strengthen the pal. By offering it to the statue of the goddess, it brings out her hidden talents.

PAL_Growth_Stone_M.item_description: A mysterious stone that can strengthen the pal. By offering it to the statue of the goddess, it brings out her hidden talents.

PAL_Growth_Stone_L.item_description: A mysterious stone that can strengthen the pal. By offering it to the statue of the goddess, it brings out her hidden talents.

PAL_Growth_Stone_XL.item_description: A mysterious stone that can strengthen the pal. By offering it to the statue of the goddess, it brings out her hidden talents.

Unko_S.item_description:
Animal dung. An essential part of any ecosystem, and can even be used as fertilizer.
It smells awful, to say the least.

Unko_L.item_description: It has an intimidating presence. Whether it's the scent or the shape, this is the mark of a heavyweight.

Sword.item_description: Sword for close-range combat. The blade is extremely sharp!

FragGrenade.item_description: A Frag Grenade useful for mid-range combat. It detonates on impact when thrown, dealing damage to enemies.

FragGrenade_Fire.item_description: Useful for mid-range combat. It detonates on impact when thrown, dealing damage and setting the surrounding environment on fire.

FragGrenade_Elec.item_description: Useful for mid-range combat. It detonates on impact when thrown, dealing damage and electrifying the surrounding environment.

FragGrenade_Ice.item_description: Useful for mid-range combat. It detonates on impact when thrown, dealing damage and freezing the surrounding environment.

Tomato.item_description: A fresh ingredient that brightens any dish. Filled with lycopene, theyre also very healthy.

WeakerBow.item_description: A bow capable of long range attacks. Hastily put together, it isn't very powerful.

Bow_Poison.item_description: A bow that poisons its target. Used with Poison Arrow.

Bow_Fire.item_description: A bow that deals Fire damage. Used with Fire Arrow.

BowGun_Poison.item_description: A Crossbow that inflicts poison on its target. It is loaded with Poison Arrows.

BowGun_Fire.item_description: A Crossbow that deals Fire damage. It is loaded with Fire Arrows.

Bow_Triple.item_description: An enhanced bow that allows three arrows to be fired simultaneously. By some strange mechanism, it only consumes a single Arrow when fired.

Bow_Fifth.item_description: An enhanced bow that allows five arrows to be fired simultaneously. By some strange mechanism, it only consumes a single Arrow when fired.

BerrySeeds.item_description:
Seeds that produce Red Berries. Necessary for starting a farm.
Can be obtained when picking Red Berries.

TomatoSeeds.item_description:
Seeds that produce Tomato. Necessary for starting a farm.
Can be purchased from a merchant.

LettuceSeeds.item_description:
Seeds that produce Lettuce. Necessary for starting a farm.
Can be purchased from a merchant.

WheatSeeds.item_description:
Seeds that produce Wheat. Necessary for starting a farm.
Can be purchased from a merchant.

Wheat.item_description: An ingredient that forms the base of various dishes. Wheat is a common crop in many parts of the world.

Flour.item_description: Flour made from grinding Wheat. It can be used as an ingredient for Bread.

Wood.item_description: Material for structures and items. Can be obtained by cutting trees.

Wool.item_description: Material sheared from sheep Pals. A necessity for creating bedding, Cloth and more.

Lettuce.item_description: A leafy green. When it comes to salad, this is a must. It has an exquisitely crunchy texture and refreshing taste.

Egg.item_description: Delicious when fried, but can also be used to cook various meals. Chikipi produce them.

Milk.item_description: Drink it as is, or use it in various meals. Can be milked from Mozzarina.

HotMilk.item_description: Even more delicious when warmed up. Great for keeping hunger away.

JamBun.item_description: A dish where jam is spread on the Bread. When consumed, it temporarily provides Defense +10%.

Salad.item_description: A Salad made by mixing Lettuce and Tomato. When consumed, it temporarily grants Attack +15%, Defense -5%.

Omelet.item_description: A dish where Egg is fried and ketchup is added. Eating it results in a temporary Attack -5%, Defense+15%.

FriedVegetables.item_description: A dish prepared by stir frying Lettuce and Raw Meat. When eaten, it will temporarily increase Attack by +10%.

HotDog.item_description: A culinary dinner sandwiching a sausage in an Bread. Consumption leads to an improved sense of fullness for a specific period.

Pancake.item_description: A dish baked by mixing Flour and Milk. It progressively decreases the rate at which one's sanity decreases when eaten.

MarinatedMushrooms.item_description: A dish made by marinating Mushroom in a marinade. Eating it temporarily increases work speed.

MushroomSoup.item_description: Cream soup made of Mushroom. When eaten, it raises the work speed and improves the stomach fullness for a certain time.

Carbonara.item_description: A dish mixing pasta with Egg and Milk. Eating it makes it harder for sanity to decrease and improves Defense by +10% for a certain amount of time.

BLT.item_description: A dish where bacon, Lettuce, Tomato are sandwiched in Bread. Consumption increases the Attack by +15% for a while.

CheeseBurger.item_description: A meal made with a Hamburger with cheese squeezed between it. Upon consumption, it increases the satiety level for a certain period as well as Defense +10%.

Pizza.item_description: A dish made by piling Red Berries, Tomato and cheese on Bread. Eating it improves Defense by +15% temporarily.

MeatSauce.item_description: A pasta dish combined with meat sauce. Eating it makes it difficult for sanity to decrease and provides Attack +10% for a while.

Cake.item_description: A dish that is eaten during celebrations. It is essential when Pals lay eggs at the breeding farm.

MushroomStew.item_description: A stew made with Mushroom. Consumption elevates work speed and offers Attack +10% for a particular duration.

Hamburger.item_description: A dish where a hamburger, Lettuce the Tomato are contained in the Bread. When eaten, it boosts one's stomach fullness and Attack by +10% for a while.

FriedEggs.item_description: An Egg now fried and even more delicious. Great for keeping hunger away.

Torch.item_description: Hold a Hand-held Torch in hand to brighten the area around you. Can also be used for close range combat in a pinch.

Glider_Old.item_description: A glider for soaring through the air. Simply made, it isn't very fast.

Glider_Good.item_description: A glider for soaring through the air. A mass produced commercial model, its decently fast.

Glider_Super.item_description: A glider for soaring through the air. With its capabilities improved, it can soar at high speeds.

Glider_Legendary.item_description: A glider for soaring through the air. Almost fast enough to keep up with airplanes.

Relic.item_description: A mysterious Pal statue that can be found all around Palpagos Island. Players can enhance their abilities by making offerings to certain statues.

Ruby.item_description: A gemstone that glows red. Can be sold to a merchant for a high price.

Sapphire.item_description: A gemstone that glows blue. Can be sold to a merchant for a high price.

Eemerald.item_description: A gemstone that glows green. Can be sold to a merchant for a high price.

Diamond.item_description: A rare gemstone that glows brilliantly. Can be sold to a merchant for a high price.

TechnologyBook_G1.item_description: A book that contains secrets of amazing technology. Use it to obtain a few Technology Points.

TechnologyBook_G2.item_description: A book that contains secrets of cutting-edge technology. Use it to obtain Technology Points.

TechnologyBook_G3.item_description: A book that contains secrets of technology beyond current day comprehension. Use it to obtain lots of Technology Points.

Meat_ChickenPal.item_description:
Chikipi meat. Light and easy to eat,
it's a local favorite for residents of Palpagos Island.

Meat_SheepBall.item_description:
Lamball meat. Red meat with a unique flavor.
Delicious, but takes some getting used to.

Meat_Kelpie.item_description:
Kelpsea meat. Tender and slightly sweet.
Fish meat tends to spoil quickly.

Meat_Eagle.item_description: Galeclaw meat. Full of nutrition, its flavor packs a punch.

Meat_Boar.item_description:
Rushoar meat. Full of the delicious flavors of wild game.
Juicy and nutritious.

Meat_LazyCatfish.item_description:
Dumud meat. Fatty with a rich taste.
Has a mouthwatering plump texture.

Meat_Deer.item_description: Eikthyrdeer meat. Light and lean, but rich in flavor.

Meat_IceDeer.item_description:
Reindrix meat. Strange venison capable of remaining at low temperatures.
Takes a very long time to spoil.

Meat_BerryGoat.item_description:
Caprity meat. Healthy and full of nutrients.
Hints of berries scenting the meat stimulates the appetite.

Meat_CowPal.item_description:
Mozzarina meat. Thick, juicy and marbled.
Residents of Palpagos Island cherish it above all other meats.

Meat_SakuraSaurus.item_description:
Broncherry meat. Giant meat full of massive stores of energy.
Stuffed to the brim with nutrients gathered through photosynthesis.

Meat_GrassMammoth.item_description:
Mammorest meat. With massive size comes massive flavor.
Its overwhelming portions are sure to satisfy any glutton.

BakedMeat_ChickenPal.item_description: Chicken skewer slow-grilled over a charcoal fire. Light and refreshing on the tongue.

BakedMeat_SheepBall.item_description: Spiced and roasted mutton. Deeply complex with unique flavors.

BakedMeat_Kelpie.item_description: Fresh fish grilled over a charcoal fire. Plump and juicy.

BakedMeat_Eagle.item_description: Grilled meat full of vitality for flying high in the skies.

BakedMeat_Boar.item_description:
Boar grilled over a hearty flame. Crispy on the outside, juicy on the inside.
Perfect as an extravagant main dish for a big party.

BakedMeat_LazyCatfish.item_description:
Grilled fish slathered with a secret sauce. Soothes both mind and body.
Perfect for tired Pal Tamers.

BakedMeat_Deer.item_description:
Carefully roasted venison with delicate flavor notes accented by the aromas of the deep forest.
Elegant taste for an elegant lifestyle.

BakedMeat_IceDeer.item_description:
When taken from a flame, Reindrix meat rapidly drops in temperature. This allows it to retain freshness for long periods of time,
making it a perfect emergency ration.

BakedMeat_BerryGoat.item_description:
Mild roast filled with the natural aromas of herbs and berries embedded in the meat.
Gives a pleasant sense of warmth when eaten outdoors.

BakedMeat_CowPal.item_description: Thick, well-done steak. Strong flavors give those who eat it an energy boost.

BakedMeat_SakuraSaurus.item_description:
Grilled meat brimming with the flavor of the king of the wilds. Juices from the compressed meat flow from the bone,
making it surprisingly tender despite the initial toughness.

BakedMeat_GrassMammoth.item_description: Boasts a rich and dignified flavor. Memories of glaciers and deep forests come rushing back with every bite.

ChickenSaute.item_description:
Plump poultry sauted in butter. Accented with fresh lemons.
Eat to slightly increase work speed for a period of time.

GrilledSheepHerbs.item_description:
Indulges in an abundance of fresh berries to create a tantalizing aroma that accentuates the unique flavor of mutton.
Eat to increase Defense by +10% for a period of time.

GenghisKhan.item_description:
Marinated mutton slow cooked over a grill. Eat to slightly increase work speed
and make SAN decrease slightly slower for a period of time.

Eaglestew.item_description: Slow-cooked dish that exudes a burst of rich, wild flavors. Eat to make SAN decrease slightly slower for a period of time.

BaconEggs.item_description:
The smoky essence of bacon intertwines flawlessly with the gentle texture of eggs, creating a sublime harmony of flavors.
Eat to increase Attack by +10% for a period of time.

StewedIceDeer.item_description:
Stewed vegetables and venison reared in a frigid environment. The meat's soft texture melts away to reveal a delicate sweetness.
Eat to stay full slightly longer for a period of time.

FriedChicken.item_description:
Magnificently juicy poultry. Eat to increase work speed
and make SAN decrease slower for a period of time.

HotDog_2.item_description:
Thick sausage wedged between warm buns. The crisply seared meat and spicy flavors are to die for.
Eat to increase Defense by +20% for a period of time.

DeerLocoMoco.item_description:
Thick hamburger steak accented with a creamy fried egg. This sublime combination brings pure joy to the mouths of those who eat it.
Eat to increase Attack by +20% for a period of time.

DeerStew.item_description:
A tender, melt-in-your-mouth venison stew crafted with love. The intertwining flavors of vegetables and meat create a harmonious blend that brings out a comforting richness.
Eat to increase Defense by +20% for a period of time.

Hamburger_2.item_description:
The rich flavor of beef melds with the sweetness of the buns in perfect harmony in this masterpiece. Eat to increase work speed
and make SAN decrease slightly slower for a period of time.

Cheeseburger_2.item_description:
Now with cheese, this dish has reached the highest level of fine cuisine. Eat to increase Attack by +20%
and stay full longer for a period of time.

FriedKelpie.item_description:
Crunchy fried batter perfectly accentuates the Kelpsea's plumpness. Eat to increase Defense by +10%
and make SAN decrease slower for a period of time.

Chowder.item_description:
Dumud lavishly covered in a thick, creamy soup. Eat to increase work speed
and stay full slightly longer for a period of time.
